576
01:02:59,930 --> 01:03:01,800
and set the coordinates for you.

577
01:03:10,260 --> 01:03:11,320
Here.

578
01:03:20,380 --> 01:03:22,300
While you are away,

579
01:03:23,350 --> 01:03:25,170
I’ll take care of the museum.

580
01:03:39,890 --> 01:03:41,460
Please take care of the museum.

581
