584
01:04:09,730 --> 01:04:13,180
(Why are they addicted to the things that will hurt them in the end?)

585
01:04:14,730 --> 01:04:20,190
(Someone is willing to sacrifice everything to have these items in their possession.)

586
01:04:20,190 --> 01:04:22,770
(It’s not because they don’t have a choice.)

587
01:04:23,070 --> 01:04:26,380
(But these items give them hope.)

588
01:04:27,520 --> 01:04:33,570
(The hope that the missing piece in their life will be fulfilled.)

589
01:04:34,130 --> 01:04:35,980
(They receive a test forcing them to choose.)

590
01:04:36,430 --> 01:04:38,370
(They have no clue what kind of result is waiting for them.)

591
01:04:39,560 --> 01:04:40,770
(Just like me.)

592
01:04:41,750 --> 01:04:43,170
(I chose to take on a journey.)

593
01:04:44,920 --> 01:04:47,430
(To look for my missing piece.)

594
01:04:49,010 --> 01:04:50,380
(I chose to leave on a journey.)

595
01:04:51,490 --> 01:04:53,970
(Not because I’m going to play in God’s game.)

596
01:04:55,070 --> 01:04:57,580
(But because someone is waiting for me.)

597
01:05:08,820 --> 01:05:10,780
(Tum told me.)

598
01:05:11,650 --> 01:05:16,780
(He believes in the marvel of science more than a myth about God.)

599
01:05:17,320 --> 01:05:21,570
(While the bible said the earth was flat,)

600
01:05:22,210 --> 01:05:25,170
(A scientist proved that the earth is round.)

601
01:05:25,780 --> 01:05:28,770
(Maybe God is not always right.)

602
01:05:29,680 --> 01:05:33,570
(We may be able to overcome the path that is predestined for us.)

603
01:05:34,500 --> 01:05:35,970
(If we have faith.)

604
01:05:37,180 --> 01:05:39,570
(We need to have faith in the path that we choose.)

605
01:05:40,960 --> 01:05:44,370
(One day, we will find happiness)

606
01:05:44,910 --> 01:05:47,100
(on the path that we choose for ourselves.)

